{"tid":1167708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國20歲華漢威脅炸毀特朗普大樓被捕 揚言槍殺示威者","createTime":"2019-05-23T08:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T07:49:28.000Z","uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"535e21002e1769f0364b48f1dfa74ff3fd8676a5","tid":1167708,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190523/_2019052316020140977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190523%2F_2019052316020140977.jpg&h=0255a2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國警方周三拘捕新澤西州一名20歲華裔男子，指他在社交網站上威脅開槍襲擊參加親以色列遊行的示威者，又揚言會放炸彈轟炸紐約市特朗普大樓。當局落案起訴他一連串罪名，包括企圖向加沙地帶恐怖組織哈馬斯提供支持、作虛假陳述及刑事恐嚇等。若全部罪名成立，他最高會被判入獄超過30年。<br />\n<br />\n被告姓謝，當局公布他的姓名為 Jonathan Xie。檢察官卡爾佩尼托形容他是「本土暴力極端分子」，對美國國家安全構成嚴峻威脅。根據控方提交上法庭的文件，謝於今年4月在社交平台 Instagram 進行串流直播，當時他戴上黑色面罩，在鏡頭前展示一枝手槍，聲稱要開槍襲擊參加親以色列遊行的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「我想向那些親以色列示威者開火......你可以拿著槍，一路開火，或者開車撞人.....需要的就是一枝槍和一輛車......我不在乎保安部隊是否捉我，他們會向我的頭顱轟一槍制止我。」同月，有人見到謝在紐約市中心的特朗普大樓外出現。<br />\n<br />\n他其後在 Instagram 上載及分享那座大樓的照片，還進行網上投票，問其他網民是否贊成他放炸彈炸掉特朗普大樓。他留言道：「OKay，我今天去過紐約市，經過特朗普大樓，失控地大笑......我忘記去以色列駐紐約領事館......我想在該處和特朗普大樓放炸彈。」<br />\n<br />\n主控官說，今年2月，謝曾表示想加入美軍，因為他想學「殺人」，但第一步先要通過背景審查。當局又控告他曾經匯錢給加沙地帶一名與哈馬斯組織一個派系有關連的人。哈馬斯已被美國政府列為恐怖主義組織。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1006811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1006811&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyoznF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=a98fc206\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1006811&h=10b7e689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1006811</a>"},{"pid":"a42f84e8877d6e0ec0e7e52625bb0b3214a1019e","tid":1167708,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"蜣國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc8b5ac8cd4e19dc5ff5030b20ccd5609503ea1","tid":1167708,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"斷佢四肢再空投返大陸啦"},{"pid":"62fc373f56ebafc627905a13e606352875a4703f","tid":1167708,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"踢佢返支那"},{"pid":"71e01ad99f6689d9ff56983fdaf77f5bda6635b7","tid":1167708,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"直接槍殺算啦"},{"pid":"cc6868464939e9c44322f9e211be6d6727499663","tid":1167708,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"on9大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8f11c83786a91e5f549f5cc76a7c58e9857907","tid":1167708,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"反以色列  就不評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d1591476313f16cb7f1c003294f30776bfc4e4","tid":1167708,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc6868464939e9c44322f9e211be6d6727499663","tid":1167708,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"on9大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:52:23.000Z","msg":"其實佢係支持個反以色列極端組織而行動<br />\n希望唔好俾中國媒體做新聞話血濃於水幫中國替天行道"},{"pid":"524d1750e41834b640244ea6879325065632c1b0","tid":1167708,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e3a6635bbb24a58406156f82ac4096f0dc658aa8","tid":1167708,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"岩，反以係正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}